                    <div class="flex">
                        <a class="mr-1" href="http://line.naver.jp/R/msg/text/?他發起重機紳士路騎：騎得慢、騎得安全、騎得帥%0D%0A https://alive.businessweekly.com.tw/Article/ARTL006001262"><img src="https://ibw.bwnet.com.tw/assets/library/alive/line_line.svg" alt="LINE分享"></a>
